- Use functional components with hooks instead of class components
- Minimize the use of `useEffect`; prefer `useCallback` and `useMemo` for optimization
- Implement proper state management using context or state management libraries
- Use `React.memo` for performance optimization of pure components
- Implement proper prop type validation using TypeScript interfaces